divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures while driving through the mountains of Pennsylvania on Route 219 near N. Cambria, PA. I was on the back of a motorcycle. I did not see the UFO until I downloaded the pictures. The 1st picture is the original photo. The 2nd photo is cropped and zoomed in.
Summary: UFO showed up in picture - did not see it when taking the picture
trends: There have been no other sightings in Dale
This sighting has never been favorited.
